quran[88]{c,v,t}:
  38,1,(s) sabaq alkalam ealaa alhrwf almqttaet fi 'awal surat albqrt
  38,2,(s) sabaq alkalam ealaa alhrwf almqttaet fi 'awal surat albqrt
  38,3,"kthyrana min al'umam 'ahlaknaha qabl hwla' almshrkyn, fastghathu hin ja'ahum aleadhab wanadawa baltwbt, walays alwaqt waqt qabwl twbt, wala waqt firar wkhlas mimaa asabhm"
  38,4,"wejib hwla' alkufaar min baeath allah 'iilayhim basharana mnhm; lydewhm 'iilaa allah wykhwwafhm edhabh, wqalu: 'iinah lays rasulana bal hu kadhib fi qwlh, sahir lqwmh, kayf ysyir alalihat alkathirat 'ilhana wahdana? 'inn hdha aladhi ja' bih wadaea 'iilayh lashy' ejyb"
  38,5,"wejib hwla' alkufaar min baeath allah 'iilayhim basharana mnhm; lydewhm 'iilaa allah wykhwwafhm edhabh, wqalu: 'iinah lays rasulana bal hu kadhib fi qwlh, sahir lqwmh, kayf ysyir alalihat alkathirat 'ilhana wahdana? 'inn hdha aladhi ja' bih wadaea 'iilayh lashy' ejyb"
  38,6,"wantalaq ruasa' alqawm wkbrawhm yhrridwn qawmahum ealaa alaistimrar ealaa alshirk walsbr ealaa taeadud alalht, wayaqulun 'iina ma ja' bih hdha alrasul shay' mdbbar yuqsad minh alriyasat walsyadt, ma samiena bima yadeu 'iilayh fi din abayina min qrysh, wala fi alnsranyt, ma hdha 'iilaa kadhab waftra'"
  38,7,"wantlq ruasa' alqawm wkbrawhm yhrridwn qawmahum ealaa alaistimrar ealaa alshirk walsbr ealaa taeadud alalht, wayaqulun 'iina ma ja' bih hdha alrasul shay' mdbbar yuqsad minh alriyasat walsyadt, ma samiena bima yadeu 'iilayh fi din abayina min qrysh, wala fi alnsranyt, ma hdha 'iilaa kadhab waftra'"
  38,8,"akhus muhamad bnzwl alquran ealayh min dwnna? bal hum fi rayb min whyy 'iilayk -ayha alrswl- w'irsaly lk, bal qaluu dhlk; li'anahum lm yadhuquu eadhab allh, falaw dhaquu eadhabah lamaa tjrwu ealaa ma qalu"
  38,9,"am hum yamlikun khazayin fadal rabik aleaziz fi sltanh, alwahhab ma yasha' min rizqih wfdlh liman yasha' min khlqh?"
  38,10,"am lhwla' almushrikin mulk alsmwat wal'ard wama bynhma, fyuetu wyamneu? flyakhdhu balasbab almwslt lahum 'iilaa alsma', hataa yhkmu bima yuridun min eata' wmne"
  38,11,"hwla' aljnd almkdhdhibwn jund mhzwmwn, kama huzm ghyrhm min al'ahzab qblhm, kdhdhabt qablahum qawm nuh waead wafireawn sahib alquat alezymt, wathamud waqawm lut wa'ashab al'ashjar walbsatyn wahum qawm sheyb. 'uwlayik al'umam aladhin thzzabu ealaa alkufr waltkdhyb wajtmeu elyh. 'in kll min hwla' 'iilaa kdhdhab alrsl, fasthqu eadhab allh, whll bihim eqabh"
  38,12,"hwla' aljnd almkdhdhibwn jund mhzwmwn, kama huzm ghyrhm min al'ahzab qblhm, kdhdhabt qablahum qawm nuh waead wafireawn sahib alquat alezymt, wathamud waqawm lut wa'ashab al'ashjar walbsatyn wahum qawm sheyb. 'uwlayik al'umam aladhin thzzabu ealaa alkufr waltkdhyb wajtmeu elyh. 'in kll min hwla' 'iilaa kdhdhab alrsl, fasthqu eadhab allh, whll bihim eqabh"
  38,13,"hwla' aljnd almkdhdhibwn jund mhzwmwn, kama huzm ghyrhm min al'ahzab qblhm, kdhdhabt qablahum qawm nuh waead wafireawn sahib alquat alezymt, wathamud waqawm lut wa'ashab al'ashjar walbsatyn wahum qawm sheyb. 'uwlayik al'umam aladhin thzzabu ealaa alkufr waltkdhyb wajtmeu elyh. 'in kll min hwla' 'iilaa kdhdhab alrsl, fasthqu eadhab allh, whll bihim eqabh"
  38,14,"hwla' aljnd almkdhdhibwn jund mhzwmwn, kama huzm ghyrhm min al'ahzab qblhm, kdhdhabt qablahum qawm nuh waead wafireawn sahib alquat alezymt, wathamud waqawm lut wa'ashab al'ashjar walbsatyn wahum qawm sheyb. 'uwlayik al'umam aladhin thzzabu ealaa alkufr waltkdhyb wajtmeu elyh. 'in kll min hwla' 'iilaa kdhdhab alrsl, fasthqu eadhab allh, whll bihim eqabh"
  38,15,"wma yantazir hwla' almushrikun lhlwl aleadhab ealayhim 'iina baquu ealaa shrkhm, 'iilaa nafkhat wahidat ma laha min rjwe"
  38,16,"wqalu: rabana ejjil lana nsybna min aleadhab fi aldyna qabl yawm alqyamt, wakan hdha asthza'an mnhm"
  38,17,"asbr -ayha alrswl- ealaa ma yqwlwnh mimaa tkrh, wadhkur eabdana dawud sahib alquat ealaa 'aeda' allah walsbr ealaa taeth, 'iinah twwab kthyr alrujue 'iilaa ma yurdi allh. (wfy hdha tslyt llrswl salaa allah ealayh wslm)"
  38,18,"'ina skhkharna aljibal mae dawud ysbbihn btsbyhh 'awal alnahar wakhrh, wasakharna altayr maeah majmueat tsbbih, wttye tbeana lh"
  38,19,"'iinaa skhkharna aljibal mae dawud ysbbihn btsbyhh 'awal alnahar wakhrh, wasakharna altayr maeah majmueat tsbbih, wttye tbeana lh"
  38,20,"wqwwayna lah mulkah balhybt walquat walnsr, wataynah alnbwt, walfsl fi alkalam walhkm"
  38,21,"whl ja'ak -ayha alrswl- khabar almtkhasimayn alldhayn tswwara ealaa dawud fi makan ebadth, fartae min dkhwlhma elyh? qaluu lh: la takhaf, fnhn khasman zalam 'ahadana alakhr, faqd baynana baledl, wala tajur ealayna fi alhkm, warshidna 'iilaa swa' alsbyl"
  38,22,"whl ja'ak -ayha alrswl- khabar almtkhasimayn alldhayn tswwara ealaa dawud fi makan ebadth, fartae min dkhwlhma elyh? qaluu lh: la takhaf, fnhn khasman zalam 'ahadana alakhr, faqd baynana baledl, wala tajur ealayna fi alhkm, warshidna 'iilaa swa' alsbyl"
  38,23,"qal ahdhma: 'iina hdha 'akhi lah tise watiseun min alneaj, walays eindi 'iilaa naejatan wahdt, ftme fyha, wqal: aetnyha, wghlbny bhjth"
  38,24,"qal dawd: laqad zalamak 'akhuk bswalh dama naejatik 'iilaa neajh, wa'iina kthyrana min alshuraka' lyetdy bedhm ealaa bed, wyzlmh bakhdh haqah wedm 'insafh min nafsih 'iilaa almuminin alsalhyn, fala ybghy bedhm ealaa bed, wahum qlyl. wayqn dawud 'anana ftnnah bhdhh alkhswmt, fastaghfar rbh, wsjd tqrbana llh, warajae 'iilayh wtab"
  38,25,"fghfrna lah dhlk, wajaealnah min almqrrabyn endna, waeddna lah hasan almasir fi alakhrt"
  38,26,"ya dawud 'iinaa astkhlfnak fi al'ard wmllaknak fyha, fahkum bayn alnaas bialeadl wal'insaf, wala tatabie alhwa fi alahkam, fyudlk dhlk ean din allah wshreh, 'iina aladhin yadillun ean sabil allah lahum eadhab 'alim fi alnar; bghflthm ean yawm aljaza' walhsab. wafi hdha tawsiat lwlat al'amr 'ana yhkmu bialhaqi almanzil min allh, tabarak wteala, wala yedlu enh, fydlu ean sbylh"
  38,27,"wama khalaqna alsama' wal'ard wama baynahuma ebthana wlhwana, dhlk znn aladhin kfru, fawayl lahum min alnaar yawm alqyamt; lznhm albatl, wakufrihim ballh"
  38,28,"anjel aladhin amanuu waeamiluu alsaalihat kalmufsidin fi alard, 'am najeal 'ahl altqwa almuminin kashab alfjwr alkafryn? hadhih altaswiat ghyr layqt bhkmt allah whukmh, fala yastawun eind allh, bal ythyb allah almuminin alatqya', wyeaqb almufsidin alashqya'"
  38,29,"hdha almwha bih 'iilayk -ayha alrswl- kitab 'anzalnah 'iilayk mbark; lytfkru fi ayath, wyemlu bhdayath wdlalath, waliatadhakar 'ashab aleqwl alsalimat ma klfhm allah bh"
  38,30,"wwhbna ldawd aibnih slyman, fanemna bih elyh, waqrrna bih eynh, niem aleabd slyman, 'iinah kan kthyr alrujue 'iilaa allah wal'inabt 'ilyh"
  38,31,"adhkr hin euridt ealayh esrana alkhywl al'asilat alsryet, taqif ealaa thlath qwaym wtrfe alrabet; lnjabtha wkhftha, fama zalat tuerd ealayh hataa ghabat alshms"
  38,32,"fqal: 'iinani atharat hubi almal ean dhikr rabiy hataa ghabat alshams ean eynyh, ruddu ely alkhayl alty eurdt min qbl, fshre ymsh swqha waenaqha"
  38,33,"fqal: 'iinani atharat hubi almal ean dhikr rabiy hataa ghabat alshams ean eynyh, ruddu ely alkhayl alty eurdt min qbl, fshre ymsh swqha waenaqha"
  38,34,"wlqd abtlyna sulayman wa'alqayna ealaa kursiuh shiqun walad, wulid lah hin 'uqsim lytwfnn ealaa nsayh, wklhn tati bfars yujahid fi sabil allh, walam yql: 'in sha' allh, fataf ealayhina jmyeana, falam tahmil minhuna 'iilaa aimra'at wahidat ja'at bishiqi wld, thuma raje sulayman 'iilaa rabih wtab, qal: rabi aghfir li dhnby, waetny mlkana ezymana khasana la yakun mithlih li'ahad min albashar bedy, 'ink- sbhank- kthyr aljwd waleta'. fastajabna lh, wdhllna alriyh tajri bi'amrih tyiet mae quatuha wshdtha hayth arad"
  38,35,"walaqad abtlyna sulayman wa'alqayna ealaa kursiuh shiqun walad, wulid lah hin 'uqsim lytwfnn ealaa nsayh, wklhn tati bfars yujahid fi sabil allh, walam yql: 'in sha' allh, fataf ealayhina jmyeana, falam tahmil minhuna 'iilaa aimra'at wahidat ja'at bishiqi wld, thuma raje sulayman 'iilaa rabih wtab, qal: rabi aghfir li dhnby, waetny mlkana ezymana khasana la yakun mithlih li'ahad min albashar bedy, 'ink- sbhank- kthyr aljwd waleta'. fastajabna lh, wdhllna alriyh tajri bi'amrih tyiet mae quatuha wshdtha hayth arad"
  38,36,"wlqd abtlyna sulayman wa'alqayna ealaa kursiuh shiqun walad, wulid lah hin 'uqsim lytwfnn ealaa nsayh, wklhn tati bfars yujahid fi sabil allh, walam yql: 'in sha' allh, fataf ealayhina jmyeana, falam tahmil minhuna 'iilaa aimra'at wahidat ja'at bishiqi wld, thuma raje sulayman 'iilaa rabih wtab, qal: rabi aghfir li dhnby, waetny mlkana ezymana khasana la yakun mithlih li'ahad min albashar bedy, 'ink- sbhank- kthyr aljwd waleta'. fastajabna lh, wdhllna alriyh tajri bi'amrih tyiet mae quatuha wshdtha hayth arad"
  38,37,"wskhkharna lah alshayatin ystemlhm fi aemalh: faminhum albnawwn walghwwaswn fi albhar, wakhrwn, wahum mrdt alshyatyn, mwthwqwn fi alaghlal. hdha almulk aleazim waltskhyr alkhasi eatawuna lak ya slyman, faet man shit wamne man shyt, la hisab elyk"
  38,38,"wskhkharna lah alshayatin ystemlhm fi aemalh: faminhum albnawwn walghwwaswn fi albhar, wakhrwn, wahum mrdt alshyatyn, mwthwqwn fi alaghlal. hdha almulk aleazim waltskhyr alkhasi eatawuna lak ya slyman, faet man shit wamne man shyt, la hisab elyk"
  38,39,"wskhkharna lah alshayatin ystemlhm fi aemalh: faminhum albnawwn walghwwaswn fi albhar, wakhrwn, wahum mrdt alshyatyn, mwthwqwn fi alaghlal. hdha almulk aleazim waltskhyr alkhasi eatawuna lak ya slyman, faet man shit wamne man shyt, la hisab elyk"
  38,40,w'in lisulayman eindana fi aldaar alakhirat laqrbtan wahusn mrje
  38,41,"wadhkr -ayha alrswl- eabdana aywb, hin daea rabah 'ana alshaytan tasabab li bteb wmshqt, walm fi jsdy wmaly wahly"
  38,42,"fqlna lh: adrib birijlik al'ard ynbe lak minha ma'an bard, fashrb mnh, waghtsil fayadhhab eank alduru waladha"
  38,43,"fkshfna eanh durah wakrmnah wawahabna lah 'ahlah min zawjat wwld, wzdnah mathaluhum binin whfdt, kl dhlk rahmatan mnna bih w'ikramana lah ealaa sbrh, webrt wdhkra li'ashab aleqwl alslymt; liaelamuu 'ana eaqibat alsabr alfrj wakashf aldr"
  38,44,"wqlna lh: khudh biadik huzmt shmarykh, fadrib biha zawjak 'ibrarana bymynk, fala thnth; 'iidh 'uqsim lydrbnnaha miayat jaldat 'iidha shfah allh, lmma ghadab ealayha min 'amr yasir 'athna' mrdh, wakanat aimra'at salht, frhmha allah wrhmh bhdhh alftwa. 'iinaa wajadna 'ayuwb sabrana ealaa albla', niem aleabd hw, 'iinah rjjae 'iilaa taeat allh"
  38,45,"wadhkr -ayha alrswl- eibadina wanbya'na: 'iibrahim wa'iishaq wyeqwb; fa'iinahum 'ashab quatan fi taeat allh, wbsyrt fi dynh"
  38,46,"'ina khssnahm bkhast ezymt, hayth jaealna dhikraa aldaar alakhirat fi qlwbhm, femlu laha btaetna, wdeu alnaas 'ilyha, wdhkkarwhm bha. wa'iinahum eindana lamin aladhin akhtarnahum ltaetna, wastfynahm lrsaltna"
  38,47,"'ina khssnahm bkhast ezymt, hayth jaealna dhikraa aldaar alakhirat fi qlwbhm, femlu laha btaetna, wdeu alnaas 'ilyha, wdhkkarwhm bha. wa'iinahum eindana lamin aladhin akhtarnahum ltaetna, wastfynahm lrsaltna"
  38,48,"wadhkur -ayha alrswl- ebadna: 'ismaeyl, walyse, wadha alkfl, bi'ahsan aldhkr; 'iina kla minhum min al'akhyar aladhin akhtarhm allah min alkhlq, wakhtar lahum 'akmal al'ahwal walsfat"
  38,49,"hdha alquran dhikr wshrf lak -ayha alrswl- wlqwmk. wa'iin li'ahl taqwaa allah wtaeth lahsn masir eindana fi janaat 'iqamt, mfttaht lahum abwabha, mutakiiyn fiha ealaa al'arayik almzyanat, yatlubun maa yashtahun min 'anwae alfwakh alkathirat walshrab, min kuli ma tashtahih nfwshm, wtldhh aeynhm"
  38,50,"hdha alquran dhikr wshrf lak -ayha alrswl- wlqwmk. wa'iin li'ahl taqwaa allah wtaeth lahsn masir eindana fi janaat 'iqamt, mfttaht lahum abwabha, mutakiiyn fiha ealaa al'arayik almzyanat, yatlubun maa yashtahun min 'anwae alfwakh alkathirat walshrab, min kuli ma tashtahih nfwshm, wtldhh aeynhm"
  38,51,"hdha alquran dhikr wshrf lak -ayha alrswl- wlqwmk. wa'iin li'ahl taqwaa allah wtaeth lahsn masir eindana fi janaat 'iqamt, mfttaht lahum abwabha, mutakiiyn fiha ealaa al'arayik almzyanat, yatlubun maa yashtahun min 'anwae alfwakh alkathirat walshrab, min kuli ma tashtahih nfwshm, wtldhh aeynhm"
  38,52,wendhm nisa' qasirat 'absarihina ealaa 'azwajahuna mtsawyat fi alsn
  38,53,"hdha alnaeim hu maa tueadun bh- 'ayuha almtqwn- yawm alqyamt, 'iinah larzqna lkm, lays lah fna' wala anqtae"
  38,54,"hdha alnaeim hu maa tueadun bh- 'ayuha almtqwn- yawm alqyamt, 'iinah larzqna lkm, lays lah fna' wala anqtae"
  38,55,"hdha aldhy sabaq wasafah llmtqyn. wa'amaa almtjawzwn alhdd fi alkufr walmeasy, falahum sharun marjie wmsyr, wahu alnaar yuedhdhabwn fyha, tghmrhm min jmye jwanbhm, fabis alfrash frashhm"
  38,56,"hdha aldhy sabaq wasafah llmtqyn. wa'amaa almtjawzwn alhdd fi alkufr walmeasy, falahum sharun marjie wmsyr, wahu alnaar yuedhdhabwn fyha, tghmrhm min jmye jwanbhm, fabis alfrash frashhm"
  38,57,"hadha aleadhab ma'an shadid alhrart, wsdyd sayil min ajsad 'ahl alnaar flyshrbwh, walahum eadhab akhar min hdha alqbyl asnaf walwan"
  38,58,"hdha aleadhab ma'an shadid alhrart, wsdyd sayil min ajsad 'ahl alnaar flyshrbwh, walahum eadhab akhar min hdha alqbyl asnaf walwan"
  38,59,"wend tward altaghyn ealaa alnaar yashtm bedhm bedana, wayaqul bedhm lbed: hadhih jamaeat min 'ahl alnaar dakhlt mekm, fyjybwn: la mrhbana bhm, wala aitasaeat manaziluhum fi alnar, 'iinahum mqaswn hrr alnaar kama qasynaha"
  38,60,"qal fawj alatbae lltaghyn: bal 'antum la mrhbana bkm; lankm qddamtm lana skna alnaar l'idlalkm lana fi aldnya, fabis dar alaistiqrar jhnm"
  38,61,"qal fawj alatbae: rabana man adllana fi aldunya ean alhudaa fdaeif eadhabah fi alnar"
  38,62,"wqal altaghwn: ma balna la naraa maeana fi alnaar rijalana kunaa naeuduhum fi aldunya min al'ashrar alashqya'? hal thqyrna lahum wasthzawna bihim khta, 'aw 'anahum maeana fi alnar, lkn lm taqae ealayhim alabsar?"
  38,63,"wqal altaghwn: ma balna la naraa maeana fi alnaar rijalana kunaa naeuduhum fi aldunya min al'ashrar alashqya'? hal thqyrna lahum wasthzawna bihim khta, 'aw 'anahum maeana fi alnar, lkn lm taqae ealayhim alabsar?"
  38,64,'in dhlk min jidal 'ahl alnaar wkhsamhm haqa waqie la miryat fyh
  38,65,"ql -ayha alrswl- lqwmk: 'iinama 'ana mundhir lakum min eadhab allah 'an yahila bkm; bsbb kfrkm bh, lays hunak 'ilh msthq llebadt 'iilaa allah whdh, fahu almtfrd bezmth wasmayh wsfath wafealh, alqhhar aldhy qhr kula shay' wghlbh"
  38,66,"malk alsmwat wal'ard wama baynahuma aleaziz fi antqamh, alghafaar ldhnwb man tab wa'anab 'iilaa mrdath"
  38,67,"ql -ayha alrswl- lqwmk: 'iina hdha alquran khabar eazim alnfe. 'antum eanh ghafilun mnsrfwn, la taemalun bh"
  38,68,"ql -ayha alrswl- lqwmk: 'iina hdha alquran khabar eazim alnfe. 'antum eanh ghafilun mnsrfwn, la taemalun bh"
  38,69,"lays li eilm bakhtsam malayikat alsama' fi shan khalaq adm, lawla telym allah 'iyay, w'iyhawh 'ilya"
  38,70,"ma yuhi allah 'ily min eilm ma la eilm li bih 'iilaa li'aniy nadhir lakum min edhabh, mbyin lakum shreh"
  38,71,"adhkr lahum -ayha alrswl-: hin qal rabuk llmlaykt: 'iiniy khaliq bshrana min tyn. fa'iidha swwayt jasadih wkhlqh wanafakht fih alrwh, fdbt fih alhyat, fasjuduu lah sjwd tahiatan w'ikram, la sjwd eibadat wtezym; falebadt la takun 'illa lilah whdh. waqad hrram allah fi shryet al'islam alsujud llthyt"
  38,72,"adhkr lahum -ayha alrswl-: hin qal rabuk llmlaykt: 'iiniy khaliq bshrana min tyn. fa'iidha swwayt jasadih wkhlqh wanafakht fih alrwh, fdbt fih alhyat, fasjuduu lah sjwd tahiatan w'ikram, la sjwd eibadat wtezym; falebadt la takun 'illa lilah whdh. waqad hrram allah fi shryet al'islam alsujud llthyt"
  38,73,"fsjd almalayikat kuluhum 'ajmaeun taeat wamtthala ghyr 'iblys; fa'iinah lm yasjud anafatan wtkbrana, wakan min alkafirin fi ealim allah teala"
  38,74,"fsjd almalayikat kuluhum 'ajmaeun taeat wamtthala ghyr 'iblys; fa'iinah lm yasjud anafatan wtkbrana, wakan min alkafirin fi ealim allah teala"
  38,75,"qal allah l'iblys: ma aldhy manaeak min alsujud liman akrmtuh fkhlqtuh bydya? 'astakbart ealaa adm, 'am kunt min almutakabirin ealaa rbk? wafi alayat 'iithbat sifat alydyn lilah tabarak wteala, ealaa alwajh allayq bih sbhanh"
  38,76,"qal 'iiblis meardana lrbh: lm asjd lh; li'anani 'afdal mnh, hayth khalaqtani min narin, wakhalaqtah min tyn. (walnar khayr min altyn)"
  38,77,"qal allah lh: fakhruj min aljanat fa'iinak mrjwm balqwl, mdhwr mlewn, wa'iina ealayk tardiin w'ibeady 'iilaa yawm alqyamt"
  38,78,"qal allah lh: fakhruj min aljanat fa'iinak mrjwm balqwl, mdhwr mlewn, wa'iina ealayk tardiin w'ibeady 'iilaa yawm alqyamt"
  38,79,"qal 'iblys: rbb fakhkhir ajly, wala thlkny 'iilaa hin tabeth alkhalq min qbwrhm"
  38,80,"qal allah lh: fa'iinak min almwkhkharyn 'iilaa yawm alwaqt almelwm, wahu yawm alnfkht al'uwlaa eindama tamut alkhlayq"
  38,81,"qal allah lh: fa'iinak min almwkhkharyn 'iilaa yawm alwaqt almelwm, wahu yawm alnfkht al'uwlaa eindama tamut alkhlayq"
  38,82,"qal 'iblys: fbeztk- ya rb- wezmtk ladlnn bani adam ajmeyn, 'iilaa man akhlstah minhum lebadtk, wesmtah min 'idlaly, falam tajeal li ealayhim sbyla"
  38,83,"qal 'iblys: fbeztk- ya rb- wezmtk ladlnn bani adam ajmeyn, 'iilaa man akhlstah minhum lebadtk, wesmtah min 'idlaly, falam tajeal li ealayhim sbyla"
  38,84,"qal allh: falhqq mny, wala 'aqul 'iilaa alhq, lamlan jahanam mink wamin dhrytk wamiman tabieak min bani adam ajmeyn"
  38,85,"qal allh: falhqq mny, wala 'aqul 'iilaa alhq, lamlan jahanam mink wamin dhrytk wamiman tabieak min bani adam ajmeyn"
  38,86,"ql -ayha alrswl- lhwla' almushrikin min qwmk: la 'atlub minkum ajrana 'aw jza'an ealaa daeawtukum whdaytkm, wala addaey amrana lays ly, bal 'atabie ma ywha 'ilya, wala 'atakalaf tkhrrusana waftra'an"
  38,87,"ma hdha alquran 'iilaa tadhkir lilealamin min aljini wal'ins, yatadhakarun bih ma yanfaeuhum min masalih dinahum wdnyahm"
  38,88,"wltelmn- 'ayuha almshrkwn- khabar hdha alquran wsdqh, hin yaghlb al'islam, wayadkhul alnaas fih afwajana, wkdhlk hin yaqae ealaykum aledhab, wtnqte eankum alasbab"